# AI SQL Query Builder - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to the root llm_engineering directory as .env and add your actual key

# OpenRouter API Key (required)
# Get your free API key at: https://openrouter.ai/
# OpenRouter provides access to 100+ AI models through one unified API
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here

# That's it! Just one API key gives you access to:
# - OpenAI GPT models (GPT-5, GPT-5-nano, etc.)
# - Anthropic Claude models (Claude Sonnet 4.5, etc.)
# - Google Gemini models (Gemini 2.5 Pro, etc.)
# - DeepSeek, Qwen, Llama, and 100+ more models
#
# No need for separate API keys for each provider!
